# NICM.SYS ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png)  ![:inline](/images/elmo.gif) 

### Description

NICM.SYS is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: f4126206-564f-49f5-a942-2138a3131e0e
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**:  | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/magicsword-io/LOLDrivers/raw/main/drivers/52b7cd123f6d1b9ed76b08f2ee7d9433.bin" "Download" >}}{{< button "https://www.magicsword.io/premium" "Block" "red" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create NICM.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\NICM.SYS type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start NICM.SYS
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
